						<p><hi rend="bold">Parāntaka I, Year 29 = 936 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Gift of 10 <hi rend="italic">kaḷañju</hi> of gold for a lamp by certain servants <hi rend="italic">(kōyiṟ-piḷḷaikaḷ)</hi> of prince Rājāditya to the temple of Āṟṟuttaḷi-Mahādēvar. The gold was received by the <hi rend="italic">ūrār</hi> of Kuchappāḍi in Muḍiyūr-nāḍu for maintaining the lamp.</p>						

